data.description: Welcome to Broadway Park Lofts. The highly desired downtown loft style  urban oasis. Directly across from Pioneer Park and Farmers Market. 1/2 block from Caputos and walking distance to the Delta Center, City Creek and all downtown entertainment. This unit has 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. The main floor has a modern kitchen with refrigerator included. A sizable living space with a industrial style garage door bringing in plenty of natural light. It can be opened to bring the outdoors  in. Upstairs has 2 bedrooms and a full bath. This is your opportunity to live in the coolest downtown space at an affordable price.  1 space in parking garage included. NO NIGHTLY RENTALS. LEASES MUST BE MIN 6 MOS. Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only. Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
